item.title: CVE-2018-1160|2024-08-05T03:51:48.914Z -- netatalk -- netatalk
item.description: Netatalk before 3.1.12 is vulnerable to an out of bounds write in dsi_opensess.c. This is due to lack of bounds checking on attacker controlled data. A remote unauthenticated attacker can leverage this vulnerability to achieve arbitrary code execution.
